'''99% Invisible'''（意思為「99％隱形」）是一個由{{le|Roman Mars|Roman Mars}}主持的獨立電台節目，內容主要關於[[設計|設計]]及[[建築|建築]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://99percentinvisible.org/about/ |title=About | 99% Invisible |publisher=99percentinvisible.org |date=2014-01-31 |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140212211134/http://99percentinvisible.org/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它最初為三藩市[[公共廣播|公共廣播]]電台{{le|KALW|KALW}}與[[美國建築師學會|美國建築師學會]]的合作項目。該節目由{{le|公共廣播交流|Public Radio Exchange}}分發到各電台廣播，以及透過互聯網[[Podcast|Podcast]]發佈，是{{le|Radiotopia|Radiotopia}}網路其中一員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://media.prx.org/PRXRadiotopia_release_FINAL.pdf |title=PRX launches Radiotopia, new podcast network of story-driven public radio shows |publisher=Media.prx.org |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221174630/http://media.prx.org/PRXRadiotopia_release_FINAL.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 概觀 ==
該節目的名稱來自[[巴克敏斯特·富勒|巴克敏斯特·富勒]]的一句話：「你其中99％都是隱形和觸摸不到的。」（Ninety-nine percent of who you are is invisible and untouchable.）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://designenvy.aiga.org/99-invisible-roman-mars/ |title=Design Envy · 99% Invisible: Roman Mars |publisher=Designenvy.aiga.org |date=2013-01-08 |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221222141/http://designenvy.aiga.org/99-invisible-roman-mars/ |archive-date=2014-02-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>該Podcast的目標是令被忽視的設計、建築及活動得到注意。每集通常都專注於一個主題或一個設計，並會訪問和該設計有關的建築師或專家。

{{as of|2014}}，99% Invisible正於第四季，並定時每週發佈一集<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://99percentinvisible.org/news/kickstart-season-4-weekly/ |title=Kickstart Season 4- Weekly! | 99% Invisible |publisher=99percentinvisible.org |date=2013-10-23 |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222011425/http://99percentinvisible.org/news/kickstart-season-4-weekly/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{as of|2015}}製作團隊包括製作人Sam Greenspan、Avery Trufelman和Katie Mingle，以及數碼總監Kurt Kohlstedt<ref>{{cite web |url=http://99percentinvisible.org/about/ |title=About | 99% Invisible |publisher=99percentinvisible.org |date=2015-12-05 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archive-date=2014-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140212211134/http://99percentinvisible.org/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
評論者的評價非常正面，節目亦受不同媒體及電台主持好評。[[This_American_Life|This American Life]]主持{{le|艾拉·格拉斯|Ira Glass}}稱該節目為「十分精彩及有趣，製作精美」（completely wonderful and entertaining and beautifully produced）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eyesin.com/architecture/2013/roman-mars-is-99-invisible/ |title=Roman Mars is 99% Invisible | Architecture |publisher=Eyes In |date=2013-04-04 |accessdate=2014-02-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222194306/http://www.eyesin.com/architecture/2013/roman-mars-is-99-invisible/ |archivedate=2014-02-22 }}</ref>，而電台節目主持{{le|Jad Abumrad|Jad Abumrad}}指該節目「擁有在普通Podcast及電台講故事找不到的節奏及音樂感」（has a kind of rhythm and musicality that you don't normally find in radio or podcast storytelling）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://junkee.com/featured-podcast-99-invisible/2273 |title=Featured Podcast: 99% Invisible |publisher=Junkee |date= |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221185122/http://junkee.com/featured-podcast-99-invisible/2273 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2013年，[[雅虎|雅虎新聞]]在它的「你應該聽的最佳Podcast」列表中包含了99% Invisible<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.yahoo.com/best-podcasts-itunes-193044509.html |title=The best podcasts you aren't listening to but should be - Yahoo News |publisher=News.yahoo.com |date=2013-07-29 |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219001220/http://news.yahoo.com/best-podcasts-itunes-193044509.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，《[[觀察家報|觀察家報]]》的Miranda Sawyer亦推薦該節目<ref>{{cite web |author=Miranda Sawyer |url=http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2013/may/26/99-per-cent-invisible-radio-review |title=Rewind Radio: 99% Invisible | Television & radio | The Observer |publisher=Theguardian.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203154721/http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2013/may/26/99-per-cent-invisible-radio-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

主持Roman Mars因99% Invisible被列為《[[快公司|快公司]]》2013年最具創意人物之一<ref>{{cite web |last=Feifer |first=Jason |url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3009142/most-creative-people-2013/63-roman-mars |title=63. Roman Mars | Fast Company | Business + Innovation |publisher=Fast Company |date=2013-05-13 |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214072427/http://www.fastcompany.com/3009142/most-creative-people-2013/63-roman-mars |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及在2014年被列入1000名最具創意人物列表<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3025456/most-creative-people/most-creative-people-in-business-1000-the-complete-list |title=Most Creative People In Business 1000: The Complete List | Fast Company | Business + Innovation |publisher=Fast Company |date=2014-01-29 |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217174705/http://www.fastcompany.com/3025456/most-creative-people/most-creative-people-in-business-1000-the-complete-list |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{as of|2014|1}}該Podcast在[[iTunes|iTunes]]排名排名前50位<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewTop?cc=us&genreId=26&popId=3 |title=iTunes Store |publisher=itunes.apple.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605174116/https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewTop?cc=us&genreId=26&popId=3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在iTunes的4000個評論中，97%的評論均評該Podcast為五星<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/99-invisible/id394775318?mt=2 |title=iTunes - Podcasts - 99% Invisible by Roman Mars |publisher=itunes.apple.com |date= |accessdate=2014-02-17 |archive-date=2014-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417182915/https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/99-invisible/id394775318?mt=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年「Structural Integrity」一集在{{le|第三屆海岸國際音頻節|Third Coast International Audio Festival}}得獎<ref>{{cite web|title=Third Coast International Audio Festival :: Structural Integirty|url=http://thirdcoastfestival.org/library/1838-and-the-winners-are|website=Third Coast International Audio Festival|accessdate=2016-05-14|archive-date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027103201/http://thirdcoastfestival.org/library/1838-and-the-winners-are|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

